snippet.title: Amber Heard Exposed by Former Personal Assistant
snippet.description:
Kate James, Amber Heard's former personal assistant, has submitted a declaration about the actress about what it was like working for her.  Specifically she states that she  never saw any violence between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, never saw Johnny beating her, nor did she see marks on Amber's face.  However, she had a lot to say about Amber's treatment of her.  She also mentioned several times in her declaration that Amber never liked anyone talking to Johnny for whatever reason...Amber was jealous and paranoid about Kate even sharing small talk with her husband.  Amber was very controlling and abusive.  
Here are some links.  @ThatBrianFella from Twitter posted all the pages to James' declaration HERE:
https://twitter.com/ThatBrianFella/status/1237841845851262978

Daily Mail Article about Kate James' Declaration and Amber's Spokesperson's Response HERE:
https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8100091/Amber-Heards-ex-assistant-claims-actress-routinely-abused-her.html
